      "para_id": "Q001383.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) After Ninimma filled ( Aya-diĝirĝu ) with awe by addressing him , Aya-diĝirĝu , father of Aka , the temple administrator of Utu , and Kumtuše , mother of Aya-diĝirĝu , dedicated ( this statue ) to Ninšubur ."
    }
  ],
